ename=L68s3aO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL68s3aO.png&h=a977e07d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPYqgDgh5yHVmedVhHS9WbRseF973eogRzjgjctWYoUEQ?filename=Z4YvWaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4YvWaC.jpg&h=67c51792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNMjha5dBpCk4E1NmfmeAiSzxgLTtbedLxayinKnTRE7C?filename=HT7WLUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHT7WLUL.jpg&h=1d282361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUFk7NJkPVNeFCZ36Q1rCTWToaCrEvYdNMjonQ4yEC52V?filename=zmohBwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmohBwW.jpg&h=c586607c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUrnVd5zwCYCsUKDu3nb1vgjiciKEKXn4KRTtWFBR4LEH?filename=YhZUq5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhZUq5S.jpg&h=f132d523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWC91E1NNBJF2ZXC1fVeNMoKYSMmjjZXomFBqJSGxmzdJ?filename=LDKumtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDKumtg.jpg&h=de3a70cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXy1LiF73jwNQidFNXU3k4xrh4FVqWieAUorM2Ecw8AGE?filename=JpZNSzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpZNSzV.jpg&h=8a51ebf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><strong><span class=\"navy\"><span class=\"x-large\">熱刺</span></span></strong>是一間座落英國倫敦北部托定咸區的職業足球會<br />\n從1882年成立至今已經擁有過百年歷史，現時競逐於英格蘭超級聯賽；<br />\n球會主場為熱刺球場，球會的拉丁文格言 &rdquo;<em>Audere est Facere (To Dare Is To Do)</em>&rdquo; 則意謂「<em>敢作敢為</em>」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><ins><strong><p class=\"center\">榮譽：</p></strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<p class=\"center\">甲組聯賽 冠軍：1950/1951、1960/1961<